{"tid":1078210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨李永達：每日150個單程證中，約30至40人是「有特別任務的共產黨員」","createTime":"2019-03-26T06:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T06:42:49.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"24a1e94969fe036821ba99e3b450dd4976bf26fc","tid":1078210,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:42:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190325/59407438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190325%2F59407438&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=e4cd88d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190325%2F59407438&h=d7b0c86a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190325/59407438</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190324/large/1553434133_4459.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190324%2Flarge%2F1553434133_4459.png&h=881b4062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年有關單程證的爭議越趨激烈，不少人質疑持單程證來港人士非全屬家庭團聚，懷疑中共以此派人滲透香港。民主黨創黨成員、佔中九子之一李永達在即將出版的回憶錄，引述一名熟悉香港保安政策並曾參與其中的權威人士資料，披露每日150個單程證中，約30至40人是「有特別任務的共產黨員」，估計過去20多年中共已滲透最少21萬地下黨員來港。"}]}